003448", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003447", "text": "Professional guidance makes choosing easier."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003450", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003449", "text": "Explore Rechargeable Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003452", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003451", "text": "Rechargeable hearing aids combine smart design, strong amplification, and easy care. With features like Bluetooth connectivity, apps, and long battery life, they support clear hearing in many environments. Choosing the right device with professional support helps ensure comfort, clarity, and confidence."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003457", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003453", "text": "If you are considering rechargeable hearing aids,"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003455", "text": "Maico Audiology", "marks": ["m003454"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003456", "text": "is here to help. Our team can guide you through options, reviews, and pricing to find the best solution for your hearing needs."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m003454", "href": "/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003459", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003458", "text": "Contact us today to schedule an appointment!"}]}]','{"id": "01KS5SXJZKDSCCPN4M2GDGVG2C", "src": "/_emdash/api/media/file/01KS5SXJV95K407A8Z4E5GF4D1.jpg", "alt": ""}','Rechargeable Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Learn about rechargeable hearing aids, features, price, and apps. Schedule a hearing test at Maico Audiology today.');
INSERT INTO "ec_blog_post" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","publish_date","author","category","content","featured_image","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MNXG5CF0XFF7476JCPT','swimmers-ear','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21T22:53:37.984Z','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,2,'01KS6BX11CV0WTB1HTJCVR6H5S',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MNXG5CF0XFF7476JCPT','Understanding Swimmer’s Ear: Causes, Symptoms, and Safe Treatment','November 13, 2025','Tracey E. Hudson, Au.D., CCC-A','Hearing','[{"_type":"block","_key":"b003464","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003460","text":"Swimmer’s ear is a painful and uncomfortable condition that can cause itchiness, drainage, and hearing changes after water gets trapped in the ear canal. It often affects people who spend time in the water, but anyone can develop it. At Maico Audiological Services, with offices in Newport News, Smithfield, and Chesapeake, VA, our audiologists help patients find relief from swimmer’s ear and other hearing concerns through","marks":["strong","em"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003462","text":"hearing tests","marks":["m003461","strong","em"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003463","text":", prevention tips, and professional guidance.","marks":["strong","em"]}],"markDefs":[{"_type":"link","_key":"m003461","href":"/audiology-services/hearing-tests/"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003466","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003465","text":"What Is Swimmer’s Ear?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003468","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003467","text":"Swimmer’s ear, also known as otitis externa, is an infection or inflammation of the outer ear canal-the passage that runs from the outside of your ear to your eardrum. It usually occurs when water stays trapped inside the ear after swimming, showering, or bathing. This trapped moisture creates the perfect environment for bacteria or fungi to grow."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003470","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003469","text":"Although the name “swimmer’s ear” might make you think it only affects swimmers, that’s not always the case. It can happen to anyone exposed to moisture or humidity for extended periods. Even activities like sweating heavily or cleaning your ears too often can make the ear canal more vulnerable."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003472","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003471","text":"Audiologists often see patients, both frequent swimmers and non-swimmers, who develop itchiness, pain, or fullness in the ear after water exposure. Understanding what causes it can help you take steps to prevent it."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003474","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003473","text":"What Causes Swimmer’s Ear?"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003476","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003475","text":"Swimmer’s ear develops when moisture, injury, or irritation disrupts the natural protective layer inside your ear canal. Once that protective barrier breaks down, bacteria or fungi can grow and lead to infection."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003478","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003477","text":"Here are the most common causes and risk factors:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003480","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003479","text":"1. Water Exposure","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003482","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003481","text":"When water remains trapped in your ear canal after swimming, showering, or bathing, it increases humidity inside the ear. This warm, damp environment helps bacteria or fungi multiply."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003484","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003483","text":"2. Ear Canal Injury","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003486","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003485","text":"Inserting cotton swabs, fingers, or small objects into your ear can scratch the delicate skin, making it easier for germs to enter. Even minor irritation can trigger an infection."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003488","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003487","text":"3. Earwax Problems","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003490","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003489","text":"Earwax plays an important role in ear health by acting as a natural barrier against dirt and bacteria. Removing too much wax can leave your ear unprotected, while excess wax can trap water inside and cause swimmer’s ear."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003492","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003491","text":"4. Climate and Humidity","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003494","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003493","text":"People who live in warm, moist areas or spend time in high humidity are more likely to develop swimmer’s ear, even if they aren’t swimmers. Moist air prevents the ear canal from drying properly."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003496","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003495","text":"5. Skin Conditions","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003498","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003497","text":"Those with eczema, psoriasis, or chronic allergies may have dry or flaky skin, which can lead to itchiness and small cracks in the ear canal, allowing bacteria to enter more easily."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003500","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003499","text":"Symptoms of Swimmer’s Ear"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003502","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003501","text":"The symptoms of swimmer’s ear can range from mild irritation to severe pain. Recognizing them early helps you get the right treatment before complications occur."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003504","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003503","text":"Common signs include:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003506","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003505","text":"Itchiness inside the ear canal (one of the earliest symptoms)"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003508","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003507","text":"Ear pain that worsens when pulling on the ear or moving the jaw"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003510","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003509","text":"Fullness or pressure in the ear"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003512","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003511","text":"Redness or swelling around the outer ear"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003514","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003513","text":"Fluid drainage, which may be clear, yellow, or pus-like"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003516","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003515","text":"Muffled hearing or a sensation that the ear is “blocked”"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003518","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003517","text":"Tenderness when touching the ear or surrounding area"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003520","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003519","text":"Fever or swollen glands near the ear (in advanced cases)"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003522","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003521","text":"If left untreated, swimmer’s ear can cause more severe infection or temporary hearing loss. That’s why seeing an audiologist or doctor promptly is important when symptoms persist."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003527","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003523","text":"Maico Audiological Services connects you to an expert"},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003525","text":"audiologist in Newport News, VA","marks":["m003524"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003526","text":", Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA."}],"markDefs":[{"_type":"link","_key":"m003524","href":"/audiologist-hearing-aids-newport-news-va/"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003529","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003528","text":"How Swimmer’s Ear Is Diagnosed"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003531","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003530","text":"Diagnosing swimmer’s ear is simple, gentle, and pain-free. Here’s an overview:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003533","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003532","text":"Medical History:","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003535","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003534","text":"We’ll ask about recent water exposure, ear symptoms, or prior infections. Ear Examination:","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003537","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003536","text":"Using a lighted tool called an otoscope, your audiologist will look inside the ear canal for redness, swelling, wax, or fluid buildup."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003539","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003538","text":"Cleaning (if needed):","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003541","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003540","text":"If wax or debris is blocking the view, we may safely remove it for a clearer examination. If the infection looks severe or involves deeper tissue, your audiologist may refer you to your doctor or an ear, nose, and throat specialist for additional care."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003543","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003542","text":"Treatment for Swimmer’s Ear"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003545","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003544","text":"Treatment for swimmer’s ear focuses on clearing the infection, reducing itchiness and pain, and helping the ear heal. Most cases resolve quickly with the right care."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003547","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003546","text":"1. Cleaning the Ear Canal","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003549","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003548","text":"Gently removing debris or excess wax helps medications work better. Our Smithfield, VA audiologists at Maico Audiological Services use professional tools to clean the ear safely, avoiding further irritation."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003551","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003550","text":"2. Prescription Ear Drops","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003553","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003552","text":"Antibiotic ear drops are the most common treatment for swimmer’s ear. They fight bacteria and may include a mild steroid to reduce inflammation and itching. It’s important to use them exactly as prescribed. If your infection is caused by a fungus, antifungal drops may be used instead."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003555","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003554","text":"3. Oral Antibiotics","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003557","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003556","text":"In more serious infections or cases where the infection spreads beyond the ear canal, your doctor may prescribe oral antibiotics to help your body fight the infection from within."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003559","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003558","text":"4. Pain and Inflammation Relief","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003561","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003560","text":"Over-the-counter pain relievers like acetaminophen or ibuprofen can reduce discomfort while the infection heals."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003563","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003562","text":"5. Keeping the Ear Dry","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003565","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003564","text":"Avoid swimming, diving, or soaking your ears during treatment. When showering, protect the ear with a soft earplug or cotton ball lightly coated with petroleum jelly. With the right treatment and follow-up, most patients start feeling relief within a few days."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003567","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003566","text":"Prevention: How to Avoid Swimmer’s Ear"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003569","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003568","text":"Preventing swimmer’s ear is often easier than treating it. A few simple habits can protect your ears and reduce the risk of infection."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003571","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003570","text":"1. Keep Your Ears Dry","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003573","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003572","text":"After swimming or bathing, gently tilt your head to each side to let water drain. Pat your outer ear dry with a towel-don’t insert anything into the canal."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003575","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003574","text":"2. Protect Ears While Swimming","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003577","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003576","text":"Frequent swimmers can benefit from custom-fitted swim earplugs, available through our offices in Newport News, Smithfield, and Chesapeake, VA. These keep water out while maintaining comfort and sound clarity."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003579","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003578","text":"3. Avoid Overcleaning","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003581","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003580","text":"Cleaning too deeply removes protective earwax and increases the risk of itchiness and infection. If you feel blocked, visit an audiologist for professional cleaning."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003583","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003582","text":"4. Manage Humidity and Sweat","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003585","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003584","text":"If you live in a high-humidity area or sweat frequently, let your ears air out after exercise or outdoor activities. Wearing breathable headgear can also help reduce trapped moisture."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003587","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003586","text":"5. Use Preventive Drops","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003589","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003588","text":"Ask your audiologist or doctor about safe, over-the-counter drying drops to use after swimming. These help remove leftover moisture and prevent bacterial growth."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003591","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003590","text":"When to See an Audiologist or Doctor"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003593","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003592","text":"While mild cases can improve with home care, persistent symptoms should be evaluated by a professional."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003595","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003594","text":"You should schedule an appointment if you experience:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003597","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003596","text":"Ongoing itchiness or ear pain"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003599","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003598","text":"Drainage or swelling that worsens"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003601","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003600","text":"Reduced or muffled hearing"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003603","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003602","text":"A feeling of fullness or blockage"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003605","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003604","text":"Fever or spreading redness"}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003607","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003606","text":"At Maico Audiological Services, we’ll determine whether your swimmer’s ear is caused by bacteria, fungus, or another issue, and we’ll recommend safe, effective treatment options."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003609","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003608","text":"Living Comfortably After Swimmer’s Ear"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003611","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003610","text":"Once your ear heals, it’s important to protect it from future infections."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003613","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003612","text":"Here’s how:"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003615","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003614","text":"Keep your ears clean but avoid inserting objects into them."}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003617","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003616","text":"Dry your ears after every swim or shower."}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003619","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003618","text":"Treat colds, allergies, and sinus congestion early to prevent Eustachian tube problems."}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003621","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003620","text":"Be mindful of humidity, especially during summer months or in moist environments."}],"listItem":"bullet","level":1},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003623","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003622","text":"Our team at Maico Audiological Services is here to help you maintain ear comfort and hearing wellness year-round."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003625","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003624","text":"Frequently Asked Questions"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003627","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003626","text":"Is swimmer’s ear contagious?","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003629","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003628","text":"No, swimmer’s ear is not contagious. It’s caused by bacteria or fungi that grow inside a person’s ear canal, usually because of trapped water, irritation, or too much moisture. You can’t catch it from swimming near someone with an infection or sharing water."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003631","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003630","text":"However, if you share earbuds, towels, or earplugs, you could spread bacteria that may increase the risk of infection. Keeping ears clean and dry helps prevent it from developing."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003633","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003632","text":"How long does swimmer’s ear last?","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003635","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003634","text":"With proper treatment, swimmer’s ear usually starts improving within a few days and clears up completely in 7 to 10 days. The length of recovery depends on how severe the infection is and how quickly treatment begins. Using prescribed antibiotic ear drops as directed by your doctor and keeping your ear dry during healing can help it clear faster. If symptoms, such as itchiness, pain, or drainage, don’t improve after a week, follow up with your audiologist or healthcare provider for another evaluation."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003637","style":"h3","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003636","text":"What happens if swimmer’s ear goes untreated?","marks":["em"]}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003639","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003638","text":"If swimmer’s ear is left untreated, the infection can worsen and spread deeper into the ear canal or surrounding tissue. This may cause increased pain, swelling, earache, or even temporary hearing loss. In severe cases, the infection could reach nearby bones or lymph nodes, requiring stronger antibiotics or medical intervention. Early treatment is the best remedy. It relieves symptoms faster and prevents complications. If you notice persistent discomfort, drainage, or hearing changes, schedule a consultation with an audiologist or doctor as soon as possible."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003641","style":"h2","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003640","text":"Expert Audiologists in Virginia"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003643","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003642","text":"If you’re struggling with swimmer’s ear, don’t wait for symptoms to worsen. The earlier you seek treatment, the easier it is to relieve pain, stop itchiness, and prevent infection from spreading."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003648","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003644","text":"At"},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003646","text":"Maico Audiological Services","marks":["m003645"]},{"_type":"span","_key":"s003647","text":", we proudly serve the communities of Newport News, Smithfield, and Chesapeake, VA, providing compassionate care for patients of all ages. Whether you’re an active swimmer or simply someone experiencing ear discomfort, our experienced audiologists can help."}],"markDefs":[{"_type":"link","_key":"m003645","href":"/"}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003650","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003649","text":"We offer professional ear examinations, safe ear cleanings, and guidance on treatment options, including when to see your doctor for antibiotics or additional care."}]},{"_type":"block","_key":"b003652","style":"normal","children":[{"_type":"span","_key":"s003651","text":"Call Maico Audiological Services today to schedule your appointment. With expert care, preventive strategies, and personalized support, you can recover from swimmer’s ear quickly and get back to enjoying the water comfortably and safely."}]}]','{"id":"01KS5SXTXQT8DF8BN2RM3H51KW","alt":"","provider":"local","filename":"assets__media__Understanding-Swimmers-Ear-Causes-Symptoms-and-Safe-Treatment-1bdfec1919.jpg","mimeType":"image/jpeg","meta":{"storageKey":"01KS5SXTVNQE1G4ECJ0GMXHBCN.jpg","caption":null,"blurhash":"L9GT4[.m00E,v-?b57%2DiWF$e-6","dominantColor":"rgb(132,164,167)"}}','Understanding Swimmer''s Ear: Causes, Symptoms, and Safe Treatment | Maico Audiological Services','If you’re struggling with swimmer’s ear, don’t wait for symptoms to worsen. Call Maico Audiological Services today to schedule your appointment with an audiologist.');
INSERT INTO "ec_blog_post" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","publish_date","author","category","content","featured_image","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MPTATY0WF37K9M12KF3','the-best-way-to-clean-your-ears','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MPT6723THQJ1CYNNXYZ',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MPTATY0WF37K9M12KF3','The Best Way to Clean Your Ears','June 9, 2025','Tracey E. Hudson, Au.D., CCC-A','Hearing','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b003654", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003653", "text": "Safe ear cleaning means keeping the outside of your ears clean and letting your earwax do its job, while only removing wax when it causes a blockage or symptoms."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003656", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003655", "text": "Cotton swabs and ear candles can push wax deeper or injure the ear canal and eardrum, but simple at-home steps and professional removal can relieve clogging and protect your hearing."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003658", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003657", "text": "Maico Audiological Services provides safe earwax checks, professional earwax removal, and hearing tests in Newport News, Chesapeake, and Smithfield, VA."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003661", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003659", "text": "One of the most common questions we hear is,"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003660", "text": "“What’s the best way to clean my ears?”", "marks": ["em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003663", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003662", "text": "Many people think they need to clean their ears often, but the truth is your ears are very good at cleaning themselves. Still, sometimes earwax can build up and cause discomfort, and it’s important to know the safe way to handle it."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003665", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003664", "text": "Why Do We Have Earwax?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003667", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003666", "text": "Earwax may not seem pleasant, but it actually plays an important role in keeping your ears healthy. It:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003669", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003668", "text": "Protects the ear canal from dust, dirt, and germs"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003671", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003670", "text": "Keeps the skin inside the ear from getting dry or itchy"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003673", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003672", "text": "Helps fight off bacteria and infection"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003675", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003674", "text": "Most of the time, earwax slowly moves out of the ear on its own and falls away naturally."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003679", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003676", "text": "What You Should"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003677", "text": "Not", "marks": ["em"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003678", "text": "Do"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003681", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003680", "text": "Many people reach for cotton swabs or other objects to clean their ears. This can actually push earwax deeper, causing blockages, pain, or even injury to the eardrum. Other risky methods include ear candles, which are not safe or effective and can burn the skin or cause serious damage."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003683", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003682", "text": "Safe Ways to Clean Your Ears at Home"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003685", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003684", "text": "If your ears feel a little clogged, here are some safe steps you can try at home:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003687", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003686", "text": "Wipe the Outer Ear", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003689", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003688", "text": "Use a soft cloth to gently wipe the outside of your ear after a shower. This is usually all that is needed."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003691", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003690", "text": "Use Warm Water", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003693", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003692", "text": "Letting warm water run over your ears while you shower can help loosen and wash away small amounts of wax."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003695", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003694", "text": "Try Ear Drops", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003697", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003696", "text": "Over-the-counter ear drops or a few drops of mineral oil, baby oil, or hydrogen peroxide can soften wax so it comes out more easily."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003699", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003698", "text": "When to See a Professional"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003704", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003700", "text": "Sometimes earwax builds up too much and causes problems like hearing loss, earaches, ringing in the ears ("}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003702", "text": "tinnitus", "marks": ["m003701"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003703", "text": "), or a feeling of fullness. When this happens, it’s best to see a hearing professional."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m003701", "href": "/audiology-services/tinnitus-support/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003706", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003705", "text": "Audiologists can safely and gently perform professional earwax removal. This process is quick, comfortable, and much safer than trying to do it on your own."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003711", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003707", "text": "Maico Audiological Services connects you to expert audiologists providing hearing tests and"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003709", "text": "hearing aids in Chesapeake, VA", "marks": ["m003708"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003710", "text": ", and nearby locations."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m003708", "href": "/audiologist-hearing-aids-chesapeake-va/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003713", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003712", "text": "Protecting Your Ears for the Future"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003715", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003714", "text": "To keep your ears healthy:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003717", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003716", "text": "Avoid sticking objects in your ears"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003719", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003718", "text": "Use hearing protection in noisy places"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003721", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003720", "text": "Have your ears checked if you notice pain, pressure, or sudden changes in hearing"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003723", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003722", "text": "Remember, a little earwax is normal and healthy. Only clean your ears when there is a problem, and always do it safely."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003725", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003724", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003727", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003726", "text": "Can earwax cause hearing loss?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003729", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003728", "text": "Yes. If earwax builds up enough to block your ear canal, it can make sounds seem muffled or harder to hear. Removing the blockage usually brings relief."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003731", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003730", "text": "How often should I clean my ears?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003733", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003732", "text": "For most people, wiping the outside of the ear during a shower is enough. You don’t need to clean inside your ears unless a doctor or audiologist recommends it."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003735", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003734", "text": "Is it safe to use cotton swabs?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003737", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003736", "text": "No. Cotton swabs can push earwax deeper and may even injure your ear. They should never be used inside the ear canal."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003739", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003738", "text": "Can earwax cause ear pain or ringing?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003741", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003740", "text": "Yes. A buildup of wax can create pressure, which sometimes leads to discomfort, pain, or even tinnitus (ringing in the ears)."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003743", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003742", "text": "Schedule a Consultation with Trusted Audiologists in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003745", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003744", "text": "If you feel like your ears are clogged or you’re not hearing as well as you should, you may need to see an audiologist for a check up or a hearing test."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b003750", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s003746", "text": "Call"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003748", "text": "Maico Audiological Services", "marks": ["m003747"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s003749", "text": "to be connected to expert audiologists and hearing instrument specialists in Newport News, Chesapeake, or Smithfield, VA."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m003747", "href": "/"}]}]','{"id": "01KS5SXP00ZDQ0AW1D8J0NWAX5", "src": "/_emdash/api/media/file/01KS5SXNQWQ43GRA7RW2648EG3.jpg", "alt": ""}','The Best Way to Clean Your Ears | Maico Audiological Services','Wondering how to clean your ears safely? Maico Audiological Services in Newport News, Chesapeake & Smithfield can help. Call us today!');
INSERT INTO "ec_contact_page" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","content_body","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5QZ4D840RSMCJ1CDAJF1JD','contact','published',NULL,NULL,'2026-05-21T17:05:12.104Z','2026-05-22T06:36:19Z','2026-05-21T17:05:12.104Z',NULL,NULL,1,'1973086a5be54e82a364eccdadabb68a',NULL,'en','01KS5QZ4D840RSMCJ1CDAJF1JD','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b7f97cc669414141b41a", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "f9e2fa30b830472ca665", "text": "Let?s Help You Hear Life Clearly!", "marks": []}], "markDefs": []}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "221aca0a5d04465293ab", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "503f3fcf587f49f08d57", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we make it simple to get started. Whether you have questions about hearing aids, need help with insurance, or want to schedule your hearing test, our friendly team is here for you.", "marks": []}], "markDefs": []}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "a09108f1bdeb48e28a37", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "b6982aabc11d44b38eae", "text": "Schedule your appointment today at one of our three office locations", "marks": []}], "markDefs": []}]','Contact - Maico Audiological Services','Contact Maico Audiological Services in Virginia for hearing tests, hearing aid support, and expert care. Call or send a message to connect with us today.');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MAXMZYGCYZ1PKHSH6RC','hearing-aid/phonak','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MAXHHPNVB8Y8WW6QJSE',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MAXMZYGCYZ1PKHSH6RC','Phonak Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b000002", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000001", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Phonak hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake VA, and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["strong", "em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000006", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000003", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we’re proud to offer Phonak hearing aids, a world leader in hearing technology. Phonak’s philosophy,"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000004", "text": "“Well-Hearing is Well-Being,”", "marks": ["em"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000005", "text": "reflects their belief that better hearing means a better life. With innovative features like Bluetooth streaming, rechargeable batteries, water resistance, and powerful speech clarity, Phonak creates solutions for every lifestyle and every level of hearing loss. Whether you’re new to hearing aids or looking to upgrade, our audiologist or hearing instrument specialists will help you find the Phonak device that keeps you connected, comfortable, and confident."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000008", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000007", "text": "Phonak Hearing Aids In Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000010", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000009", "text": "Phonak Infinio Ultra Line"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000012", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000011", "text": "The Phonak Infinio Ultra Line represents the next evolution in hearing technology, delivering elevated clarity, efficiency, and adaptability through advanced AI processing. Released in October 2025, this flagship upgrade enhances the foundational Infinio platform with smarter sound recognition, better battery performance, and simplified maintenance."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000014", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000013", "text": "For many existing Phonak users, these improvements can be activated through an in-clinic firmware update, allowing current Infinio or Infinio Sphere devices to perform at an entirely new level without requiring new hardware."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000016", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000015", "text": "Infinio Ultra R"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000018", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000017", "text": "A flexible, ultra-adaptive model powered by AutoSense OS™ 7.0, designed to automatically adjust to a wide range of environments. Ideal for patients seeking seamless performance in everyday listening."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000020", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000019", "text": "Infinio Ultra Sphere"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000022", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000021", "text": "Engineered for complex and noisy situations, this model features Spheric Speech Clarity 2.0 and the breakthrough DEEPSONIC™ AI chip, the world’s first dedicated processor for real-time speech separation. This allows clearer understanding of multiple speakers from any direction, even in the most challenging soundscapes."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000024", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000023", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000027", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000025", "text": "AutoSense OS™ 7.0", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000026", "text": "adapts with 24% greater precision and is trained on 18× more sound scenarios, resulting in smarter environmental transitions and more natural listening."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000030", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000028", "text": "Spheric Speech Clarity 2.0", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000029", "text": "(Ultra Sphere only) enhances speech up to threefold in noisy settings by isolating voices and reducing background interference."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000034", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000031", "text": "Listening effort is reduced by up to"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000032", "text": "35%", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000033", "text": ", supporting long-term comfort and decreasing auditory fatigue."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000036", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000035", "text": "Phonak Virto Infinio"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000038", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000037", "text": "Phonak Virto Infinio is a custom in-the-ear (ITE) hearing aid released in 2025, built for those who want powerful performance in a discreet design. Each device is custom-molded to match the shape of your ear, giving you a snug, comfortable fit that lasts all day."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000040", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000039", "text": "Packed with advanced sound technology, Virto Infinio delivers clear, natural hearing in a small, almost invisible shell, perfect for anyone who wants great sound without drawing attention."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000042", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000041", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000045", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000043", "text": "Custom-Made Fit:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000044", "text": "Each device is individually molded to the shape of your ear, ensuring a secure, comfortable fit that’s easy to wear all day."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000048", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000046", "text": "AutoSense OS 6.0:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000047", "text": "Automatically adjusts settings based on your surroundings, providing seamless hearing whether you’re in quiet, noisy, or dynamic environments."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000051", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000049", "text": "Durable & Water-Resistant:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000050", "text": "Rated IP68 for dust and moisture resistance, making it ideal for active lifestyles and daily wear."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000054", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000052", "text": "Multiple Technology Levels:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000053", "text": "Available in four tiers (I90, I70, I50, I30) to meet a range of hearing needs and budgets."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000056", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000055", "text": "Phonak Audéo Sphere"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000058", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000057", "text": "The Phonak Audéo Sphere is designed to give you clear, natural sound and easy listening, whether your hearing loss is mild or more severe. It automatically adapts to your surroundings, helping you follow conversations in noisy restaurants, chat one-on-one, or enjoy your favorite music with comfort and clarity. A key benefit of the Audéo Sphere is its rechargeable battery, which lasts all day on a single charge."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000060", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000059", "text": "From morning until night, you can count on reliable performance without the hassle of swapping batteries. It also offers wireless smartphone connection, so you can answer calls, stream music, and adjust your hearing aid settings right from an easy-to-use app."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000062", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000061", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000065", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000063", "text": "Dedicated AI chip:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000064", "text": "Smartly separates speech from noise."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000068", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000066", "text": "Automatic sound adaptation:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000067", "text": "Automatically adjusts to different listening environments."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000071", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000069", "text": "Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000070", "text": "Connects with smartphones for hands-free calls, streaming, and remote control through an app."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000073", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000072", "text": "Phonak Audéo™ Infinio"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000075", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000074", "text": "The Phonak Audéo Infinio is built to make everyday listening easier and more enjoyable. With advanced technology, it improves speech recognition in noisy places, automatically adjusts to your surroundings, and connects seamlessly to smartphones and other devices. The result is clearer conversations and less effort when listening, so you can stay engaged without feeling worn out."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000077", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000076", "text": "Designed for comfort and convenience, the Audéo Infinio offers rechargeable battery options and a slim, discreet design that fits comfortably behind the ear. It’s perfect for all-day wear, keeping you connected and confident from morning to night."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000079", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000078", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000082", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000080", "text": "CROS Compatibility:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000081", "text": "Compatible with CROS for unilateral hearing loss."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000085", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000083", "text": "Roger Direct Ready:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000084", "text": "Comes with RogerDirect™ built in to further improve hearing performance in noise and over distance."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000088", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000086", "text": "Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000087", "text": "Allows for up to 8 Bluetooth® enabled devices to be paired while 2 can be simultaneously connected"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000090", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000089", "text": "Phonak CROS Infinio"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000092", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000091", "text": "The Phonak CROS Infinio is designed for people with single-sided deafness, helping them hear more naturally in everyday life. It works by wirelessly transmitting sound from the ear that cannot hear to the ear that can, giving you better awareness of your surroundings and making conversations easier to follow. Lightweight and discreet, the CROS Infinio is comfortable for all-day wear and pairs seamlessly with compatible Phonak hearing aids. Together, they provide a complete and effective solution for hearing loss in one ear so you can stay connected and confident in any setting."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000094", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000093", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000097", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000095", "text": "On-the-go Hearing:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000096", "text": "Provides uninterrupted, hands-free calls and streaming across 2x the distance."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000100", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000098", "text": "Rechargeable:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000099", "text": "Hear with confidence with Phonak CROS Infinio’s long-lasting rechargeable battery."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000103", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000101", "text": "Universal Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000102", "text": "Universal connectivity allows seamless integration with Bluetooth® devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000105", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000104", "text": "Phonak Virto Infinio"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000107", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000106", "text": "The Phonak Virto Infinio, released in 2025, is a custom in-the-ear (ITE) hearing aid designed for people who want powerful performance in a small, discreet style. Each device is carefully molded to the unique shape of your ear, ensuring a secure and comfortable fit you can wear confidently all day long. With advanced sound technology, the Virto Infinio provides clear, natural hearing in a nearly invisible shell. It’s the perfect choice for anyone who wants excellent sound quality and modern features without drawing attention to their hearing aids."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000109", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000108", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000112", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000110", "text": "Custom-Made Fit:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000111", "text": "Each device is individually molded to the shape of your ear, ensuring a secure, comfortable fit that’s easy to wear all day."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000115", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000113", "text": "AutoSense OS 6.0:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000114", "text": "Automatically adjusts settings based on your surroundings, providing seamless hearing whether you’re in quiet, noisy, or dynamic environments."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000118", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000116", "text": "Durable & Water-Resistant:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000117", "text": "Rated IP68 for dust and moisture resistance, making it ideal for active lifestyles and daily wear."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000121", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000119", "text": "Multiple Technology Levels:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000120", "text": "Available in four tiers (I90, I70, I50, I30) to meet a range of hearing needs and budgets."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000123", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000122", "text": "Phonak Audéo Fit"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000125", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000124", "text": "The Phonak Audéo Fit is designed for people with active lifestyles who want to stay connected to both sound and health. Along with delivering clear, natural hearing, it helps you build healthy habits by tracking steps, distance, activity levels, wearing time, and even heart rate through the easy-to-use myPhonak app."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000127", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000126", "text": "When connected to the app, Audéo Fit can show your current and resting heart rate as well as daily, weekly, monthly, and yearly heart rate trends. This makes it simple to stay on top of your health while enjoying great hearing. Available in two performance levels: Premium (P90) and Advanced (P70). The Audéo Fit gives you the right mix of technology and features to fit your lifestyle needs."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000129", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000128", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000132", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000130", "text": "Health Data Tracker:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000131", "text": "It enables users to track metrics such as distance traveled, steps taken, activity levels, average wearing time of the hearing aid, and heart rate. This is accessed through the myPhonak app, providing users with valuable insights into their overall well-being and helping them to maintain healthy habits."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000135", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000133", "text": "Tap Control:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000134", "text": "With this innovative feature, users can perform actions such as answering or ending phone calls, adjusting volume levels, changing programs, or activating other settings simply by tapping on their Audéo Fit hearing aid."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000138", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000136", "text": "Universal Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000137", "text": "With universal connectivity, you can pair Audéo Fit with Bluetooth®-enabled smartphones, TVs, and Roger™ devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000140", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000139", "text": "Phonak Audéo Lumity"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000142", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000141", "text": "The Phonak Audéo Lumity is built with the updated AutoSense OS™ 5.0 combined with artificial intelligence. This smart technology allows Lumity to recognize different sound environments and adjust automatically, giving you natural, clear sound in everyday situations-whether you’re at home, in a busy restaurant, or outdoors."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000144", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000143", "text": "Designed for people with mild to profound hearing loss, the Audéo Lumity is a receiver-in-the-ear (RITE) style and comes in a rechargeable model for all-day convenience. Lumity is the second generation of the world’s first waterproof rechargeable hearing aid. That makes it a perfect choice if you live an active lifestyle or want the peace of mind that your hearing aids can keep up with your day."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000146", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000145", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000149", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000147", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000148", "text": "Audéo Lumity pairs with the myPhonak app and Bluetooth-enabled devices to help you connect with the world around you."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000152", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000150", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000151", "text": "The myPhonak app is a free, easy-to-use smartphone app that empowers you to take control of your hearing. This allows you to directly connect to your Phonak hearing aids for volume control, program adjustments, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000155", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000153", "text": "Remote Help:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000154", "text": "The myPhonak app also allows you to connect virtually to remotely schedule a visit with your hearing care professional to address your hearing aid concerns."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000157", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000156", "text": "Phonak Slim"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000159", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000158", "text": "The Phonak Slim offers the same advanced technology as the Phonak Audéo Lumity, but with a sleek, redefined design. Its ergonomic shape provides improved comfort and style, fitting naturally behind the ear even if you wear glasses or face masks."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000161", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000160", "text": "This modern design gives you confidence while still delivering powerful performance. Phonak Slim hearing aids are recommended for people with mild to severe hearing loss. They are a receiver-in-the-ear (RITE) style and come in a rechargeable model, giving you all-day convenience without the hassle of changing batteries."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000163", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000162", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000166", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000164", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000165", "text": "Phonak Slim pairs with the myPhonak app and Bluetooth-enabled devices to help you connect with the world around you."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000169", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000167", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000168", "text": "The myPhonak app is a free, easy-to-use smartphone app that empowers you to take control of your hearing. This allows you to directly connect to your Phonak hearing aids for volume control, program adjustments, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000172", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000170", "text": "Remote Help:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000171", "text": "The myPhonak app also allows you to connect virtually to remotely schedule a visit with your hearing care professional to address your hearing aid concerns."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000174", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000173", "text": "Phonak CROS Lumity"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000176", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000175", "text": "Living with single-sided hearing loss or deafness can make everyday listening difficult. Background noise can feel overwhelming, and knowing where sounds are coming from isn’t always easy. The Phonak CROS Lumity is designed to overcome these challenges by sending sound from your non-hearing ear to your better-hearing ear. This lets you follow conversations no matter which side they come from, helping you stay connected and engaged in every moment."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000178", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000177", "text": "Built with the latest CROS technology, the Phonak CROS Lumity provides a seamless and natural listening experience for people with unaidable hearing loss in one ear. This device is recommended for single-sided hearing loss (SSD) and can be paired with a variety of Phonak models including Audéo L-R, Audéo L-RT, Naída L-PR, and Sky L-PR. Talk to our audiologist or hearing instrument specialist in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, or Smithfield, VA to learn more."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000180", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000179", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000183", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000181", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000182", "text": "The Phonak CROS Lumity pairs with the myPhonak app and Bluetooth-enabled devices to help you connect with the world around you."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000186", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000184", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000185", "text": "The myPhonak app is a free, easy-to-use smartphone app that empowers you to take control of your hearing. This allows you to directly connect to your Phonak hearing aids for volume control, program adjustments, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000189", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000187", "text": "Remote Help:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000188", "text": "The myPhonak app also allows you to connect virtually to remotely schedule a visit with your hearing care professional to address your hearing aid concerns."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000191", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000190", "text": "Phonak Naída Lumity"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000193", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000192", "text": "The Phonak Naída Lumity is Phonak’s most powerful hearing aid, designed for people with severe to profound hearing loss. Using advanced technology, it scans your environment up to 700 times per second, giving you clear, detailed sound quality in every setting. Built for strong and dependable performance, the Naída Lumity provides the robust volume needed to manage significant hearing loss. It comes in a behind-the-ear (BTE) style, offering comfort, reliability, and the confidence to stay connected in daily life."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000195", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000194", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000198", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000196", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000197", "text": "Naída Lumity pairs with the myPhonak app and Bluetooth-enabled devices to help you connect with the world around you."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000201", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000199", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000200", "text": "The myPhonak app is a free, easy-to-use smartphone app that empowers you to take control of your hearing. This allows you to directly connect to your Phonak hearing aids for volume control, program adjustments, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000204", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000202", "text": "Remote Help:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000203", "text": "The myPhonak app also allows you to connect virtually to remotely schedule a visit with your hearing care professional to address your hearing aid concerns."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000206", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000205", "text": "Phonak Sky Lumity"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000208", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000207", "text": "The Phonak Sky Lumity is designed with children in mind, using advanced SmartSpeech™ Technology to reduce unwanted noise and make speech easier to understand. Clear speech is especially important for early learning, growth, and cognitive development, and Sky Lumity helps give children the best start possible. This device comes in a behind-the-ear (BTE) style and is available in a rechargeable model for all-day convenience. For those needing extra power, it also comes in an ultra-power (UP) version that uses a size 675 disposable battery."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000210", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000209", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000213", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000211", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000212", "text": "Sky Lumity pairs with the myPhonak Junior app and Bluetooth-enabled devices to help you connect with the world around you. Universal connectivity allows your child to enjoy listening to their personal devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000216", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000214", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000215", "text": "The myPhonak Junior app is the industry’s only dedicated pediatric app, and empowers children to personalize their hearing experience. It gives children and parents access to wearing time, but also lets children take control of the sound around them and personalize their settings in the real world."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000219", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000217", "text": "Tamper-resistant:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000218", "text": "Phonak provides styles that help keep the battery out of reach of curious fingers."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000221", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000220", "text": "Phonak Virto Paradise"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000223", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000222", "text": "The Phonak Virto Paradise is a custom-fit hearing aid that combines comfort, discretion, and powerful sound. Each device is molded to the unique shape of your ear, so it fits securely and blends naturally for a nearly invisible look. Powered by Phonak’s advanced Paradise technology, it delivers clear, natural sound in both quiet and noisy environments making it easier to follow conversations with less effort. The Virto Paradise also offers Bluetooth® connectivity, so you can stream phone calls, music, and TV audio directly to your hearing aids for a seamless listening experience."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000225", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000224", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000228", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000226", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000227", "text": "Virto Paradise ITE and ITC devices connect to smartphones, TVs, and more to keep up with your busy life. Additionally, you can easily switch between two paired devices with enhanced Bluetooth capabilities. Smaller products such as the CIC and IIC, offer streaming via Phonak accessories."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000231", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000229", "text": "Personalization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000230", "text": "The myPhonak app is a free, easy-to-use smartphone app that empowers you to take control of your hearing. This allows you to directly connect to your Phonak hearing aids for volume control, program adjustments, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000234", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000232", "text": "Remote Help:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000233", "text": "The myPhonak app also allows you to connect virtually to remotely schedule a visit with your hearing care professional to address your hearing aid concerns."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000236", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000235", "text": "Assistive Listening Devices & Technology by Phonak"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000238", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000237", "text": "Phonak Assistive Listening Devices (ALDs) are designed to give you an extra boost in the listening situations that hearing aids alone may not fully cover. Whether you’re trying to follow a conversation in a noisy restaurant, hear clearly in a classroom or workplace, enjoy a lecture at church, or watch TV at home, Phonak’s ALDs make communication easier and more comfortable."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000240", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000239", "text": "Roger™ Wireless Microphones"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000242", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000241", "text": "Roger microphones are designed to give you clearer speech in noisy environments or when the speaker is far away. They work by picking up a person’s voice and sending it directly to your Phonak hearing aids, cutting through background noise."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000244", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000243", "text": "TV Connectors"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000246", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000245", "text": "The TV Connector streams sound straight from your television (or other media device) into your Phonak hearing aids. This gives you crisp, clear audio without having to crank up the volume for everyone else in the room."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000248", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000247", "text": "Bluetooth® Accessories"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000250", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000249", "text": "Take hands-free phone calls, listen to music, watch videos, or join video calls all streamed directly to your hearing aids."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000252", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000251", "text": "Remote Controls"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000254", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000253", "text": "Remote controls give you quick, easy control over your hearing aids. Instead of fiddling with tiny buttons on the devices themselves, you can adjust the volume, switch programs, or mute your aids with a simple handheld remote or through the myPhonak app on your smartphone. Phonak offers additional accessories to enhance your hearing aid experience:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000256", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000255", "text": "Table Mic II"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000258", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000257", "text": "Roger Focus II"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000260", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000259", "text": "Roger for Education"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000262", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000261", "text": "Clip on Mic"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000264", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000263", "text": "TV Connector"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000266", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000265", "text": "PartnerMic"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000268", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000267", "text": "Remote Control"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000270", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000269", "text": "Older Phonak Hearing Aids We Support"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000272", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000271", "text": "These hearing aid models may still be supported for hearing aid servicing and repair by Maico Audiological Services. Please contact us for more information."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000274", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000273", "text": "Phonak Audéo Paradise"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000276", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000275", "text": "Phonak Naída Paradise"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000278", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000277", "text": "Phonak CROS Paradise"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000280", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000279", "text": "Phonak Naída Link Marvel"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000282", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000281", "text": "Phonak Sky Marvel"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000284", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000283", "text": "Phonak Audéo Marvel"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000286", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000285", "text": "Phonak Bolero B"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000288", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000287", "text": "Phonak Naída B"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000290", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000289", "text": "Phonak Virto B"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000292", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000291", "text": "Phonak Audéo B"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000294", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000293", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions About Phonak Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000296", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000295", "text": "Which Phonak hearing aid is right for me?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000298", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000297", "text": "The best model depends on your level of hearing loss, your lifestyle, and your personal preferences. Our audiologist or hearing instrument specialist at Maico Audiological Services will guide you through your options and help you choose the one that fits your needs best."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000300", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000299", "text": "Can Phonak hearing aids connect to my phone or TV?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000302", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000301", "text": "Yes! Most modern Phonak hearing aids connect directly to smartphones, tablets, and TVs using Bluetooth® technology. This means you can stream phone calls, music, and videos straight to your hearing aids for clear, hands-free listening. With the Phonak TV Connector, you can also enjoy your favorite shows and movies at the perfect volume without turning the TV up for everyone else."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000304", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000303", "text": "Are Phonak hearing aids rechargeable?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000306", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000305", "text": "Yes. Many Phonak models come with rechargeable batteries that last all day on a single charge. Simply place them in their charging case overnight, and they’ll be ready to use in the morning."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000308", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000307", "text": "Find the Right Phonak Hearing Aid in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000310", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000309", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we can help you find the Phonak hearing aid that fits your hearing needs and lifestyle. As an authorized Phonak provider in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA, we offer the latest models, expert fittings, and personalized care."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000312", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000311", "text": "Schedule your consultation today!"}]}]','Phonak Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Phonak hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MBTHKFZQQSACGV8F6ZR','hearing-aid/oticon','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MBT2RVDQG71AXP4KT4N',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MBTHKFZQQSACGV8F6ZR','Oticon Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b000314", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000313", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Oticon hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["strong", "em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000316", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000315", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we’re proud to offer Oticon hearing aids, a trusted brand with more than 100 years of innovation. Built with advanced BrainHearing™ technology, Oticon devices are designed to support the way your brain naturally makes sense of sound. The result is clearer speech, less listening effort, and a more natural hearing experience. From Bluetooth® streaming and rechargeable options to tinnitus relief features, Oticon hearing aids make it easier to stay connected, confident, and engaged in everyday life."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000318", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000317", "text": "Oticon Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000320", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000319", "text": "Oticon Zeal"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000324", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000321", "text": "Oticon Zeal is the first hearing aid designed to"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000322", "text": "do it all", "marks": ["em"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000323", "text": "while staying completely unseen. Built for people who want powerful technology in an ultra-discreet design, Zeal delivers exceptional sound clarity, all-day comfort, and seamless connectivity in one tiny device no one will notice."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000326", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000325", "text": "Zeal transforms the idea of what a hearing aid should be. Its small, nearly invisible design sits comfortably in your ear, giving you the confidence to live fully without drawing attention to your device. Powered by Oticon’s advanced BrainHearing™ technology, Zeal supports the brain’s natural way of processing sound. Enjoy clear, balanced, and comfortable hearing, even in noisy places."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000328", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000327", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000331", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000329", "text": "Made to Connect", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000330", "text": ": Stream calls, meetings, music, and more directly from your phone, Apple Watch, TV, computer, or tablet. Zeal brings your digital world to life with smooth, high-quality wireless audio."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000334", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000332", "text": "Reliable Rechargeability:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000333", "text": "No disposable batteries. With fast, dependable charging, you get all-day power that keeps up with your lifestyle."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000337", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000335", "text": "Same-Day Fitting:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000336", "text": "Zeal is designed for convenience, offering the option for same-day fitting so you can begin hearing better right away."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000339", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000338", "text": "Oticon Jet PX"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000341", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000340", "text": "The Oticon Jet PX is created for people with mild to severe hearing loss. It provides clear, natural sound that makes conversations easier to follow. One of the key benefits of the Jet PX is its wireless Bluetooth® connectivity, allowing you to stream phone calls, music, and TV audio directly into your hearing aids. It also comes in a rechargeable option, giving you all-day use on a single charge so you don’t have to worry about changing batteries. If you’re looking for a hearing aid that combines performance, convenience, and comfort, the Oticon Jet PX is an excellent choice."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000343", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000342", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000346", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000344", "text": "AI-powered OpenSound Navigator with DNN:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000345", "text": "Improves hearing with clear, natural sound."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000349", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000347", "text": "Tinnitus SoundSupport:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000348", "text": "Ideal for users with tinnitus as it gives access to customizable relief sounds."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000352", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000350", "text": "SuperShield:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000351", "text": "Quickly adapts and prevents feedback before it occurs."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000354", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000353", "text": "Oticon Own SI"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000356", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000355", "text": "The Oticon Own SI is a custom in-the-ear hearing aid designed to fit your ear shape perfectly for all-day comfort and a discreet look. It is available in multiple styles, including options that sit deep in the ear canal and are nearly invisible. Despite its small size, it’s packed with smart features like Bluetooth® connectivity for direct streaming from your smartphone, TV, or tablet. If you want a hearing solution that blends personalization, comfort, and advanced technology, the Oticon Own SI is an excellent choice."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000358", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000357", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000361", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000359", "text": "Discreet and sophisticated:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000360", "text": "Super small styles (IIC and CIC) that fit fully in your ear"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000364", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000362", "text": "BrainHearing™ technology:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000363", "text": "Helps your brain make sense of sound."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000367", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000365", "text": "Custom-fit:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000366", "text": "Built for all-day comfort, even with glasses or masks."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000370", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000368", "text": "Strong and durable:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000369", "text": "Water- and dust-resistant to last through busy days."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000372", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000371", "text": "Oticon Intent"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000374", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000373", "text": "The Oticon Intent is Oticon’s most advanced hearing aid yet, designed to deliver sound that feels natural and personal to you. Using new 4D Sensor technology, it can detect your movements, surroundings, and even the way you engage in conversations. This allows the device to adjust automatically, helping you hear more clearly in every situation. Ideal for people with mild to severe hearing loss, the Oticon Intent combines smart technology with everyday convenience, helping you enjoy the sounds and conversations that matter most."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000376", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000375", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000379", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000377", "text": "Bluetooth®", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000378", "text": "LE Audio for seamless, low-energy streaming"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000382", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000380", "text": "Self-Calibrating", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000381", "text": "Speaker for optimized sound clarity"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000385", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000383", "text": "Fast Charging:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000384", "text": "33% quicker recharge for all-day use"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000387", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000386", "text": "Oticon Real"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000389", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000388", "text": "The Oticon Real is designed to bring you closer to the sounds of everyday life with clarity and comfort. Built with BrainHearing™ technology, it helps your brain process sound naturally, so conversations feel easier to follow and listening takes less effort. What sets Oticon Real apart is its ability to handle sudden, loud, or disruptive sounds. Features like Wind & Handling Stabilizer and SuddenSound Stabilizer keep unexpected noises under control without blocking out the sounds you need to hear. This means clearer speech, less distraction, and a more natural listening experience in any environment."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000391", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000390", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000393", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000392", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming for iPhone® and Android™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000395", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000394", "text": "App control via Oticon Companion or ON app"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000397", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000396", "text": "Tinnitus SoundSupport™ for calming tinnitus relief"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000399", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000398", "text": "Oticon Own"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000401", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000400", "text": "The Oticon Own is a custom in-the-ear (ITE) hearing aid designed to fit your ears perfectly for comfort and a nearly invisible look. Each device is molded to the shape of your ear, so it feels natural, stays secure, and can be worn all day with confidence. Designed for people with mild to severe hearing loss, the Oticon Own gives you a balance of discretion, comfort, and advanced technology. It’s a great choice if you want powerful performance in a device that blends seamlessly into your lifestyle."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000403", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000402", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000405", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000404", "text": "Bluetooth® compatibility with iPhone® and Android™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000407", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000406", "text": "Remote adjustments via Oticon apps"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000409", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000408", "text": "Built-in tinnitus relief with SoundSupport™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000411", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000410", "text": "Oticon Zircon"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000413", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000412", "text": "The Oticon Zircon brings the benefits of Oticon’s advanced technology to a value-friendly hearing aid. Built with BrainHearing™ technology, it helps your brain process sound more naturally so you can enjoy clearer conversations and easier listening in everyday life. The Oticon Zircon combines everyday performance with modern convenience, making it a smart choice if you want clearer sound and easy features at an approachable price."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000415", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000414", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000417", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000416", "text": "Direct Bluetooth® streaming"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000419", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000418", "text": "Control through Oticon Companion and ON app"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000421", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000420", "text": "SoundSupport™ for tinnitus management"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000423", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000422", "text": "Oticon CROS"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000425", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000424", "text": "The Oticon CROS is designed for people with single-sided deafness (SSD) who cannot benefit from a hearing aid in one ear. It works by picking up sounds from your non-hearing side and sending them wirelessly to a hearing aid on your better ear. This helps you hear more naturally, stay aware of what’s happening around you, and follow conversations no matter which side they come from. It is lightweight, discreet, and comfortable for all-day wear. It’s a powerful solution for anyone living with hearing loss in one ear who wants better awareness, easier communication, and more confidence in everyday situations."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000427", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000426", "text": "Compatible With:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000429", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000428", "text": "Oticon Real™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000431", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000430", "text": "More™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000433", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000432", "text": "Zircon™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000435", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000434", "text": "Opn S™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000437", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000436", "text": "Play PX™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000439", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000438", "text": "Xceed™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000441", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000440", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000443", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000442", "text": "TwinLink™ Bluetooth® for streaming and sound transmission"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000445", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000444", "text": "App-based remote control"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000447", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000446", "text": "Built-in tinnitus support"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000449", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000448", "text": "Oticon Play PX"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000451", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000450", "text": "The Oticon Play PX is the world’s first pediatric hearing aid with a deep neural network (DNN) technology that’s modeled after how the brain learns and makes sense of sound. Play PX helps support speech understanding and language development, known as key parts of learning and growing. It reduces background noise, enhances speech, and gives kids access to the full sound picture they need to explore, connect, and thrive."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000453", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000452", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000455", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000454", "text": "Tamper-resistant battery doors"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000457", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000456", "text": "Water & dust resistance (IP68-rated)"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000459", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000458", "text": "LED indicators for battery status"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000461", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000460", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming to smartphones and tablets"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000463", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000462", "text": "Accessories for Kids:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000466", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000464", "text": "EduMic", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000465", "text": "– A teacher-worn mic for classroom clarity"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000469", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000467", "text": "Amigo FM", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000468", "text": "– Enhances understanding in noisy settings"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000472", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000470", "text": "ConnectClip", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000471", "text": "– Wireless streaming up to 65 feet"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000474", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000473", "text": "Oticon Xceed"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000476", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000475", "text": "The Oticon Xceed is one of the world’s most powerful hearing aids, built for people with severe to profound hearing loss. It provides strong, reliable sound while still keeping speech clear and natural, helping you stay connected to the people and moments that matter most. The Oticon Xceed comes in a behind-the-ear (BTE) style, with both rechargeable and traditional battery options. Designed for those who need the highest level of amplification, the Oticon Xceed delivers power, clarity, and comfort, helping you enjoy more confidence in everyday conversations and activities."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000478", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000477", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000480", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000479", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming for calls and media"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000482", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000481", "text": "Real-time adjustments via app"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000484", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000483", "text": "Tinnitus relief with SoundSupport™"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000486", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000485", "text": "Available in rechargeable and disposable models"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000488", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000487", "text": "Assistive Listening Devices & Technology by Oticon"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000490", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000489", "text": "ConnectClip"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000492", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000491", "text": "Remote Control"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000494", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000493", "text": "Streamer Pro"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000496", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000495", "text": "TV Adapter"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000498", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000497", "text": "Older Oticon Hearing Aids We Support"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000500", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000499", "text": "The hearing aid models below may still be supported for hearing aid servicing and repair by Maico Audiological Services in in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA and Smithfield, VA. Please contact us for more information."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000502", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000501", "text": "Oticon Opn"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000504", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000503", "text": "Oticon Opn Play"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000506", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000505", "text": "Oticon Opn S"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000508", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000507", "text": "Oticon Ruby"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000510", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000509", "text": "Oticon Siya"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000512", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000511", "text": "Oticon More"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000514", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000513", "text": "If you have an older Oticon model and need support, we’re here to help!"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000516", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000515", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions About Oticon Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000518", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000517", "text": "How long do Oticon hearing aids last?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000520", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000519", "text": "With proper care, most Oticon hearing aids last about 5 to 7 years. Their lifespan depends on how often you use them, how well they’re maintained, your daily environment, and whether you choose to update to newer technology. With regular cleaning and professional checkups, your Oticon hearing aids can give you many years of reliable performance before it’s time to replace them."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000522", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000521", "text": "What is Oticon’s newest hearing aid?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000529", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000523", "text": "Released in January 2026, the"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000524", "text": "Oticon Zeal"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000525", "text": "is currently Oticon’s most modern hearing solution for those seeking total discretion."}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000526", "text": "It eliminates the historical trade-off between size and capability by including high-fidelity streaming, hands-free calling, and"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000527", "text": "SmartCharger"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000528", "text": "compatibility in a device that sits entirely within the ear canal."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000531", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000530", "text": "Are Oticon hearing aids rechargeable?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000533", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000532", "text": "Yes! Many Oticon models come with built-in rechargeable batteries that give you a full day of power on a single charge. Simply place them in their charger overnight, and they’ll be ready to go in the morning, no tiny batteries to replace. Rechargeable models are especially convenient for active lifestyles and those who want an easy, eco-friendly option."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000535", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000534", "text": "Find the Right Oticon Hearing Aid in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000537", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000536", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we can help you find the Oticon hearing aid that fits your hearing needs and lifestyle. As an authorized Oticon provider in Smithfield, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Newport News, VA, we offer the latest models, expert fittings, and personalized care."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000539", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000538", "text": "Schedule your consultation today!"}]}]','Oticon Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Oticon hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MCMS0KZ84EGFA9VCKTW','hearing-aid/resound','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MCMNB6ASK529P4RHAV3',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MCMS0KZ84EGFA9VCKTW','ReSound Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b000541", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000540", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of ReSound hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["strong", "em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000546", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000542", "text": "ReSound hearing aids are designed to help you hear clearly in both quiet and noisy environments, while also offering modern features like Bluetooth® streaming, rechargeable batteries, and tinnitus support. With options to fit mild to profound hearing loss,"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000544", "text": "ReSound hearing aids", "marks": ["m000543"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000545", "text": "make it easier to stay connected, confident, and in control of your hearing every day."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m000543", "href": "https://www.resound.com/en-us/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000548", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000547", "text": "ReSound Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000550", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000549", "text": "ReSound Enzo IA"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000552", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000551", "text": "The ReSound Enzo IA is designed for severe to profound hearing loss. It is the world’s smallest rechargeable Super Power hearing aid and the first of its kind to support Bluetooth LE Audio and Auracast broadcast streaming."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000554", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000553", "text": "With a stylish, durable design, the ReSound Enzo IA is built for the most challenging listening situations. It offers exceptional clarity, feedback control, and all-day battery life."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000556", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000555", "text": "Unique Perks and Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000559", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000557", "text": "Clear Focus:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000558", "text": "Automatically reduces background noise while highlighting speech."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000562", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000560", "text": "360 All-Around listening:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000561", "text": "Naturally shifts attention between voices and surrounding sounds."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000565", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000563", "text": "Comfortable and weatherproof:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000564", "text": "Lightweight, all-day wear with protective nanocoating."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000568", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000566", "text": "Flexible connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000567", "text": "Supports Bluetooth® LE Audio, Auracast™, and direct streaming from multiple devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000570", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000569", "text": "ReSound Vivia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000572", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000571", "text": "The ReSound Vivia delivers clear, natural sound in a variety of listening environments. Built on ReSound’s latest platform, it uses advanced sound processing and artificial intelligence (AI) to intelligently adjust to your surroundings. It also has All Access Directionality feature to help you focus on speech while still being aware of sounds around you. The Ultra Focus mode gives you an extra boost when listening to someone directly in front of you in challenging situations. Hear conversations with ease in noisy places, enjoy music, or follow dialogue on TV without needing to turn up the volume in uncomfortably loud levels."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000574", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000573", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000576", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000575", "text": "Long-lasting battery (even while streaming)"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000578", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000577", "text": "Durable, weather-resistant"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000580", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000579", "text": "Bluetooth and Auracast for smooth device and public audio connections"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000582", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000581", "text": "Auracast Assistant for hearing announcements in public venues"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000584", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000583", "text": "ReSound Savi"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000586", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000585", "text": "ReSound Savi brings excellent sound quality, comfort, and the latest wireless features at an accessible price point. It boasts of all-day power for streaming and listening and also comes with Bluetooth® & Auracast™ technology."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000588", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000587", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000590", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000589", "text": "Water and dust resistance"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000592", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000591", "text": "Auracast Assistant for public audio access"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000594", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000593", "text": "Hands-free calling with a simple tap"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000596", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000595", "text": "ReSound Nexia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000598", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000597", "text": "The ReSound Nexia combines exceptional sound clarity with powerful, high-tech connectivity. It is the first hearing aid line to support Bluetooth LE Audio and Auracast broadcast audio. Stream audio directly in public spaces like theaters, airports, or places of worship with no extra receiver needed. This is recommended for people with mild to profound hearing loss."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000600", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000599", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000602", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000601", "text": "Advanced Bluetooth® for efficient streaming and long battery life"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000604", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000603", "text": "Auracast™ to hear public broadcasts directly through your hearing aids"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000606", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000605", "text": "Smart 3D App for remote support, tinnitus management, and sound adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000608", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000607", "text": "CROS system compatibility for single-sided hearing loss"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000610", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000609", "text": "ReSound Omnia RIE & Mini RIE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000612", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000611", "text": "ReSound Omnia is ideal for mild to severe hearing loss. Available in Receiver-in-Ear (RIE) and Mini RIE designs, these devices are designed for speech clarity, all-day comfort, and natural sound."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000614", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000613", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000616", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000615", "text": "Bluetooth for hands-free calls and media streaming (iOS & Android)"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000618", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000617", "text": "“Check My Fit” tool for correct device placement"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000620", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000619", "text": "Remote app access for adjustments and tinnitus support"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000622", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_k