g design, comfort, and sound quality. Whether you have moderate, severe, or profound hearing loss, the Omnia BTE family offers a dependable, durable option that fits busy and active lifestyles."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000642", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000641", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000644", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000643", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming for calls and media"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000646", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000645", "text": "“Check My Fit” tool for optimal placement"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000648", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000647", "text": "Smart 3D App for personalized adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000650", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000649", "text": "Tinnitus therapy options for added relief"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000652", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000651", "text": "ReSound Accessories & Assistive Technology"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000654", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000653", "text": "Enhance your hearing experience with these versatile ReSound accessories:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000657", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000655", "text": "TV Streamer 2", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000656", "text": "– Stream television audio directly to your hearing aids"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000660", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000658", "text": "Phone Clip+", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000659", "text": "– Enjoy hands-free calling and streaming from your phone"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000663", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000661", "text": "Multi Mic", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000662", "text": "– Hear better in group settings or noisy areas"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000666", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000664", "text": "Remote Control", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000665", "text": "– Adjust volume and programs without your phone"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000668", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000667", "text": "Older ReSound Hearing Aids We Support"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000670", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000669", "text": "If you’re using an older ReSound device, we’re here to support you. Maico Audiological Services may provide services and repairs for the following:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000672", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000671", "text": "ReSound Key"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000674", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000673", "text": "ReSound ONE"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000676", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000675", "text": "ReSound LiNX Quattro"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000678", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000677", "text": "ReSound LiNX 3D"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000680", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000679", "text": "ReSound LiNX 2"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000682", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000681", "text": "ReSound Enzo Q"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000684", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000683", "text": "ReSound Enzo 2"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000686", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000685", "text": "ReSound Picasso"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000688", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000687", "text": "Need a tune-up or repair? Give us a call to learn more."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000690", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000689", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions – ReSound Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000692", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000691", "text": "What are the different technology levels in ReSound hearing aids?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000694", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000693", "text": "ReSound hearing aids usually come in three technology tiers to suit a variety of needs:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000696", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000695", "text": "Level 9: most advanced features for active lifestyles and complex listening environments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000698", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000697", "text": "Level 7: a balanced mix of premium and core features"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000700", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000699", "text": "Level 5: essential functionality for everyday hearing support"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000702", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000701", "text": "Our audiologist and hearing aid specialist in Chesapeake, VA, Smithfield, VA, and Newport News, VA can help you decide which level is best for your hearing and lifestyle."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000704", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000703", "text": "How can I adjust my ReSound hearing aids?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000706", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000705", "text": "You can adjust your ReSound hearing aids in a few easy ways. Many models allow you to control volume and programs directly on the device using small buttons. You can also use the ReSound Smart 3D™ app on your smartphone to make quick changes, such as adjusting volume, switching listening programs, or fine-tuning sound for noisy environments. Some models even let your hearingcare provider make remote adjustments through the app, so you can get support without visiting the office."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000711", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000707", "text": "Contact us to learn more about available"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000709", "text": "hearing aids in Smithfield, VA", "marks": ["m000708"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000710", "text": "."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m000708", "href": "/audiologist-hearing-aids-smithfield-va/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000713", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000712", "text": "How long do ReSound hearing aids last?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000715", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000714", "text": "With proper care, most ReSound hearing aids last about 5 to 7 years. Their lifespan depends on how often you wear them, how well you maintain them, and the environments you’re in each day. Regular cleaning and professional checkups help extend their life. Many people choose to upgrade sooner to take advantage of new technology, but with good care, your ReSound hearing aids can provide many years of reliable support."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000717", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000716", "text": "Find the Right ReSound Hearing Aid in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000722", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000718", "text": "Our audiologist and hearing instrument specialist at"}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000720", "text": "Maico Audiological Services", "marks": ["m000719"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000721", "text": "can help you find a ReSound hearing aid that fits your needs, preferences, and lifestyle. As an authorized ReSound provider in Chesapeake, VA, Smithfield, VA, and Newport News, VA, we offer expert fittings, ongoing support, and access to the newest models."}], "markDefs": [{"_type": "link", "_key": "m000719", "href": "/"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000724", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000723", "text": "Contact us today to learn more about how ReSound hearing aids can help you hear your best!"}]}]','ReSound Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of ReSound hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MDDXJ8RHKQ9K202QY36','hearing-aid/starkey','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MDDT16BG1VNM60CV3VP',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MDDXJ8RHKQ9K202QY36','Starkey Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b000726", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000725", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Starkey hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["strong", "em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000728", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000727", "text": "Starkey hearing aids is a brand known for combining great sound with smart wellness features. Starkey devices not only improve hearing, but also support your overall health with options like fall detection, activity tracking, and tinnitus relief. With rechargeable models, Bluetooth® streaming, and discreet styles, Starkey hearing aids are designed to keep you connected, confident, and in control of your everyday life. At Maico Audiological Services, our audiologist and hearing instrument specialist is trained to fit and program Starkey devices so you get the best sound and comfort possible. Let us help you find the Starkey hearing aid that’s right for you!"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000730", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000729", "text": "Starkey Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000732", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000731", "text": "Starkey Omega AI"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000734", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000733", "text": "Starkey Omega AI is built with industry-leading technology that gives users powerful sound clarity and day-long comfort. Its advanced AI system constantly analyzes your surroundings to help you hear speech clearly, stay aware of important sounds, and move through different environments with ease."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000736", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000735", "text": "If you struggle with hearing in noisy places, Omega AI’s Edge Mode+ provides on-demand help by sharpening speech instantly, even in challenging spaces like restaurants, shopping centers, or family gatherings."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000738", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000737", "text": "These hearing aids are also designed for durability. With a 10x more durable waterproof coating, Omega AI can handle rain, sweat, and everyday wear without worry. Rechargeable options give all-day power, keeping you connected from morning to night."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000740", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000739", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000743", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000741", "text": "Edge Mode+:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000742", "text": "Boosts speech clarity during tough listening moments."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000746", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000744", "text": "Waterproof & Everyday-Proof:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000745", "text": "Designed for active lifestyles and all-day comfort."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000749", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000747", "text": "Auracast™ & LE Audio Ready:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000748", "text": "Allows streaming from TVs, smartphones, public announcement systems, and more."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000752", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000750", "text": "Starkey App (Now Powered by Gen AI):", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000751", "text": "Use TeleHear AI for instant, AI-based sound adjustments."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000754", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000753", "text": "Starkey Signature Series"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000756", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000755", "text": "The Starkey Signature Series are tiny, almost-invisible hearing aids offering clear and powerful, sound. They are custom-made to fit comfortably inside your ear. Enjoy conversations with friends and family and feel confident knowing your hearing aids are hidden from view."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000758", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000757", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000761", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000759", "text": "Discreet:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000760", "text": "Nearly invisible and fits deep in your ear."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000764", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000762", "text": "Natural Sound:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000763", "text": "Clear, lifelike sound so you can enjoy every moment."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000767", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000765", "text": "Rechargeable:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000766", "text": "Up to 38 hours of power"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000770", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000768", "text": "Waterproof:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000769", "text": "Designed to handle water up to 1 meter deep."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000773", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000771", "text": "Custom Fit:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000772", "text": "Made just for your ears for all-day comfort and security."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000775", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000774", "text": "Starkey Edge AI"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000777", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000776", "text": "The Starkey Edge AI is a smart hearing aid that is built with powerful artificial intelligence (AI), it gives you clear, natural hearing in all kinds of environments. With just a simple tap, the Edge Mode feature can instantly adjust your settings to help you hear better in tough listening situations, like noisy restaurants or busy family gatherings. What makes the Edge AI unique is its combination of hearing and wellness features. Along with excellent sound quality, it can track your physical activity, monitor brain health, and even send fall alerts to loved ones for extra peace of mind. Perfect for people with mild to severe hearing loss, the Starkey Edge AI is a smart choice if you want advanced hearing technology that also supports your overall well-being."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000779", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000778", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000781", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000780", "text": "Sweat-resistant and waterproof up to one meter"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000783", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000782", "text": "Strong Bluetooth® connection for streaming from phones, TVs, and Auracast™ systems"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000785", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000784", "text": "Health tracking tools, including fall detection and balance exercises"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000787", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000786", "text": "My Starkey app for personalized settings, call streaming, and device location"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000789", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000788", "text": "Starkey Genesis AI RIC"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000791", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000790", "text": "The Starkey Genesis AI RIC is a modern receiver-in-canal hearing aid designed to give you clear, natural sound in every part of your day. Powered by Starkey’s AI-driven sound processing, it quickly adjusts to your surroundings so speech stays sharp and background noise doesn’t get in the way. This is recommended for people with mild to severe hearing loss and is a smart choice for anyone who wants powerful hearing support combined with advanced health and lifestyle features."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000793", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000792", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000795", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000794", "text": "Up to 51 hours of battery life on a full charge"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000797", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000796", "text": "Seven-minute quick charge provides up to three hours of use"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000799", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000798", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming and app-based control with My Starkey"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000801", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000800", "text": "TeleHear remote support for at-home adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000803", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000802", "text": "Tinnitus relief with customizable sound therapy"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000805", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000804", "text": "Water-resistant design for daily reliability"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000807", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000806", "text": "Starkey Genesis AI ITE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000809", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000808", "text": "Starkey Genesis AI ITE hearing aids are powered by advanced artificial intelligence (AI). They can adjust automatically to changes in your environment, making speech easier to understand as they easily reduce and filter unnecessary background noise. These custom hearing aids offer a comfortable and discreet listening experience."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000811", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000810", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000813", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000812", "text": "Choice between rechargeable and traditional battery models"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000815", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000814", "text": "Includes one of the smallest wireless CIC options available"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000817", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000816", "text": "Remote adjustments through the My Starkey app and TeleHear"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000819", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000818", "text": "Personalized tinnitus therapy built into each device"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000821", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000820", "text": "Durable, water-resistant construction"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000823", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000822", "text": "Starkey CROS System"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000825", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000824", "text": "The Starkey CROS System addresses hearing loss in one ear by picking up sound from your weaker ear and sending it to your better ear. Hear confidently from all directions as the CROS system helps you follow conversations, enjoy group settings, and feel more connected to the people around you. Starkey CROS is comfortable to wear, discreet, and available in styles that match your hearing needs."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000827", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000826", "text": "Compatible With:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000829", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000828", "text": "Starkey Genesis AI models"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000831", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000830", "text": "Select earlier Starkey hearing aid models"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000833", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000832", "text": "Starkey Evolv AI BTE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000835", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000834", "text": "The Starkey Evolv AI BTE is a powerful behind-the-ear hearing aid designed to give you clear, natural sound with less effort. Using AI sound processing, it automatically reduces background noise and sharpens speech, so conversations feel easier and more comfortable. Recommended for people with moderate to severe hearing loss, the Starkey Evolv AI BTE combines strong amplification with advanced smart features. Stay connected, safe, and confident every day!"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000837", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000836", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000839", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000838", "text": "Bluetooth® streaming and control via the Thrive app"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000841", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000840", "text": "TeleHear virtual support for remote adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000843", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000842", "text": "Tinnitus therapy options to help manage ringing in the ears"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000845", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000844", "text": "Starkey Evolv AI Power Plus BTE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000847", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000846", "text": "The Starkey Evolv AI Power Plus BTE is one of Starkey’s strongest hearing aids. It is designed for people with severe to profound hearing loss. With powerful amplification and AI-driven sound processing, it delivers clear, natural sound while reducing background noise, making conversations easier to follow in any environment. The Evolv AI Power Plus BTE also comes with Starkey’s wellness features. It can track your physical activity, monitor brain health, and provide fall detection alerts, helping you stay safe and connected."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000849", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000848", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000851", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000850", "text": "Uses long-lasting size 13 batteries"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000853", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000852", "text": "Thrive app compatibility for customized settings"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000855", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000854", "text": "Integrated tinnitus relief features"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000857", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000856", "text": "Virtual adjustments through remote support"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000859", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000858", "text": "Starkey Accessories & Assistive Technology"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000861", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000860", "text": "Enhance your hearing experience with a range of Starkey wireless accessories:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000864", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000862", "text": "Mini Remote Microphone:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000863", "text": "Great for clear one-on-one conversations"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000867", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000865", "text": "Remote Mic+:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000866", "text": "Streams audio from Bluetooth-enabled devices"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000870", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000868", "text": "Remote Control 2.0:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000869", "text": "Lets you easily manage volume and settings"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000873", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000871", "text": "Table Microphone:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000872", "text": "Picks up speech in group settings"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000876", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000874", "text": "TV Streamer:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000875", "text": "Sends audio directly from your TV to your hearing aids"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000878", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000877", "text": "Older Starkey Hearing Aids We Support"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000880", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000879", "text": "If you have an older Starkey hearing aid, we may still be able to service or repair it."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000882", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000881", "text": "Starkey Picasso"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000884", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000883", "text": "Starkey Livio"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000886", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000885", "text": "Starkey Muse iQ"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000888", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000887", "text": "Starkey Halo iQ"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000890", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000889", "text": "Starkey Halo 2"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000892", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000891", "text": "Starkey Halo"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000894", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000893", "text": "Please contact us for more details."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000896", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000895", "text": "FAQs – Starkey Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000898", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000897", "text": "How long do Starkey hearing aids last?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000900", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000899", "text": "Starkey hearing aids usually last about three to five years. How long they work depends on how often you use them and how well you care for them. Regular cleaning and checkups with your hearing care provider may also help your hearing aids last longer."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000902", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000901", "text": "Are Starkey hearing aids rechargeable?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000904", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000903", "text": "Yes! Many Starkey hearing aids are available in rechargeable models. These devices provide a full day of power on a single charge so you can wear them from morning to night without worrying about changing tiny batteries. Simply place them in their charging case overnight, and they’ll be ready to go the next day. Talk to our audiologist or hearing instrument specialist in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA to learn more."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000906", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000905", "text": "Can I stream phone calls and music with Starkey hearing aids?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000908", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000907", "text": "Yes! Most modern Starkey hearing aids come with Bluetooth® connectivity, which means you can stream phone calls, music, podcasts, and even TV audio directly into your hearing aids."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000910", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000909", "text": "Starkey Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000912", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000911", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Starkey hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA. Let our audiologist or hearing instrument specialist help you find the Starkey solution that best fits your hearing needs and lifestyle!"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000914", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000913", "text": "Schedule your hearing consultation today!"}]}]','Starkey Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Starkey hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1ME6Y2EQBDJETP7V7JZ6','hearing-aid/unitron','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1ME6TQJ176GXQ9D4V7P4',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1ME6Y2EQBDJETP7V7JZ6','Unitron Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b000916", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000915", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Unitron hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["em", "strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000918", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000917", "text": "Unitron is a brand known for comfort, smart design, and easy use. Unitron devices adapt to your surroundings automatically, giving you smooth, natural hearing whether you’re at home, at work, or in a busy restaurant. With modern features like rechargeable batteries, Bluetooth® streaming, and app-based controls, Unitron hearing aids make it simple to stay connected, confident, and comfortable every day. At Maico Audiological Services, our audiologist and hearing instrument specialist will help you choose the best Unitron model for your lifestyle and make sure it’s fitted for your best possible hearing."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000920", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000919", "text": "Unitron Hearing Aids In Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000922", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000921", "text": "Unitron Insera S-R"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000924", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000923", "text": "Powered by the advanced Smile platform, the Insera S-R is meticulously crafted to fit the unique contours of your ear, offering a discreet design without compromising on power. Whether you’re in a crowded restaurant or a quiet home, its AI-driven technology automatically adjusts to your environment, making hearing feel natural and effortless."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000926", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000925", "text": "It comes with robust Bluetooth connectivity and all-day battery life to help you stay connected to the people and devices that matter most."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000928", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000927", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000931", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000929", "text": "EarMatch™ Customization:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000930", "text": "An evolved design process that uses deep-fit modeling and intentional microphone placement to optimize sound performance specifically for your unique ear anatomy."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000934", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000932", "text": "Universal Bluetooth® Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000933", "text": "Enjoy stable, hands-free calls and high-quality media streaming. The Insera S-R features up to 6x more wireless transmission power and double the connection range of previous models."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000937", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000935", "text": "Rechargeable Custom Fit:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000936", "text": "Combines the “invisible” appeal of a custom-molded hearing aid with the modern convenience of lithium-ion reliability and a magnetic “snap-and-charge” docking station."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000940", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000938", "text": "HyperFocus & Speech Enhancement:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000939", "text": "Advanced spatial features that zoom in on speech during loud conversations while reducing the listening effort required in quieter settings to prevent “listening fatigue.”"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000943", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000941", "text": "IP68-Rated Durability:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000942", "text": "Engineered for everyday life with proven wax protection and a rugged, water-resistant design that ensures dependable performance in all conditions."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000945", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000944", "text": "Unitron Moxi S-R"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000947", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000946", "text": "The Unitron Moxi S-R is a sleek, rechargeable hearing aid designed for comfort and convenience. With its slim design, it sits comfortably behind the ear while delivering clear, natural sound in every situation. The Unitron Moxi S-R is powered by Unitron’s newest Smile platform and is designed for people with mild to severe hearing loss. The Unitron Moxi S-R is a great choice if you want clear sound, easy technology, and reliable comfort in a modern hearing aid."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000949", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000948", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000952", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000950", "text": "Water-Resistant:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000951", "text": "Special coating helps protect from moisture."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000955", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000953", "text": "Easy Charging:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000954", "text": "Simple charging at home or on-the-go with ChargerGo."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000958", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000956", "text": "All-Day Power:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000957", "text": "Keeps up with your busy life without running out of charge."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000960", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000959", "text": "Unitron Ativo"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000962", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000961", "text": "The Unitron Ativo is a modern hearing aid designed to make listening easy, natural, and comfortable in every part of your day. Built with Unitron’s advanced sound technology, Ativo automatically adjusts to different environments, helping you enjoy conversations at home, in noisy restaurants, or outdoors without constantly changing settings."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000964", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000963", "text": "Unique Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000967", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000965", "text": "Bluetooth Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000966", "text": "Take calls and stream sound straight from your phone."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000970", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000968", "text": "Clear Sound:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000969", "text": "Enjoy Unitron’s reliable sound performance in any setting."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000973", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000971", "text": "Hands-Free Calling:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000972", "text": "Talk on the phone without holding it up."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000976", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000974", "text": "Stylish and Comfortable:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000975", "text": "Designed to look good and feel good all day."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000979", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000977", "text": "Affordable Quality:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000978", "text": "Great technology at an easy-to-access price."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000981", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000980", "text": "Unitron Moxi V-RS"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000983", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000982", "text": "The Unitron Moxi V-RS has a slim and modern shape. It fits discreetly behind the ear and is easy to wear with glasses or masks. The Moxi V-RS automatically adapts to your surroundings, making speech clearer and background noise easier to manage. Designed for people with mild to severe hearing loss, the Moxi V-RS combines clear sound, sleek design, and modern features, helping you hear and live with confidence."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000985", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000984", "text": "Unique Perks and Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000988", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000986", "text": "Bluetooth Connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000987", "text": "With Made For All compatibility and hands-free technology, the Moxi V-RS allows seamless streaming from your favorite Bluetooth-enabled devices. Whether you’re taking calls, listening to music, or watching videos, the audio streams directly to your hearing aids without the need for extra accessories."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000991", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000989", "text": "App/Remote Help", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000990", "text": ": The Remote Plus App lets you take control of your hearing experience. You can easily adjust volume, change settings, and fine-tune your hearing aids based on your environment. For added convenience, Remote Care Assistance allows your hearing healthcare provider to make adjustments remotely, ensuring your devices are always optimized for your hearing needs."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000994", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000992", "text": "Rechargeable Convenience", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s000993", "text": ": The Moxi V-RS comes with a rechargeable option, meaning no more hassle of changing disposable batteries. Simply place your hearing aids in the charger, and enjoy a full day of power after just one charge."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000996", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000995", "text": "Unitron Moxi Vivante (V)"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b000998", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000997", "text": "Moxi V enhances speech from all directions, even in the most challenging environments. When speech is coming from the front, the smart noise reduction feature further reduces background noise for conversations even in the most complex situations. The Vivante platform flawlessly makes the subtle nuances of speech more pronounced, significantly reducing listening effort. Unitron Moxi V hearing aids are recommended for mild-to-profound hearing losses."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001000", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s000999", "text": "Unique Perks and Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001003", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001001", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001002", "text": "With Made For All compatibility and true hands-free technology, you can stream directly to your hearing aids using your favorite Bluetooth-capable devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001006", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001004", "text": "App / Remote Help", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001005", "text": ": The Remote Plus App is available for you to customize your listening experience. Whether you need to adjust volume, change settings, or stream music, you can fine-tune your devices to your specific needs. Additionally, Remote Care Assistance is available to have your hearing healthcare provider make adjustments remotely via the app."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001009", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001007", "text": "Tinnitus Relief:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001008", "text": "A noise generator is available to provide a sound enrichment source that stimulates the auditory system."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001011", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001010", "text": "Unitron Stride Blu (B)"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001013", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001012", "text": "The Unitron Stride Blu (B) is a reliable behind-the-ear hearing aid that delivers clear, powerful, and natural sound for people with moderate to severe hearing loss. Designed with comfort and durability in mind, it offers Bluetooth® streaming, rechargeable batteries, and simple app controls to make daily listening easier. Recommended for individuals with mild to profound hearing loss, the Stride Blu (B) is a dependable choice for strong performance and everyday convenience."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001015", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001014", "text": "Unique Perks and Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001018", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001016", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001017", "text": "With Made For All compatibility and true hands-free technology, you can stream directly to your hearing aids using your favorite Bluetooth-capable devices."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001021", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001019", "text": "App / Remote Help", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001020", "text": ": The Remote Plus App is available for you to customize your listening experience. Whether you need to adjust volume, change settings, or stream music, you can fine-tune your devices to your specific needs. Additionally, Remote Care Assistance is available to have your hearing healthcare provider make adjustments remotely via the app."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001024", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001022", "text": "Tinnitus Relief:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001023", "text": "A noise generator is available to provide a sound enrichment source that stimulates the auditory system."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001026", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001025", "text": "Unitron Stride Blu (B) UP"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001028", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001027", "