e": "span", "_key": "s001093", "text": "Unitron Stride P R"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001096", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001095", "text": "Unitron Max SP"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001098", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001097", "text": "Unitron Max UP"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001100", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001099", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions About Unitron Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001102", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001101", "text": "What is the Unitron Smile?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001104", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001103", "text": "The Unitron Smile is Unitron’s latest and most advanced hearing aid platform, launched in 2025. It’s designed to make listening feel effortless and natural. Hearing aids built on the Smile platform are easy to hear with, easy to wear, and simple to use."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001106", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001105", "text": "This system uses AI technology to automatically adjust sound to your environment. It can recognize and adapt to eight different listening situations, giving you clearer hearing with less effort and fewer manual changes."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001108", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001107", "text": "What are the levels of technology in Unitron?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001110", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001109", "text": "Unitron offers hearing aids in four main technology levels, each with different features to match your needs:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001112", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001111", "text": "Level 3 – Essential"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001114", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001113", "text": "Level 5 – Standard"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001116", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001115", "text": "Level 7 – Advanced"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001118", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001117", "text": "Level 9 – Premium"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001120", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001119", "text": "The higher the level, the more advanced the hearing aid is at reducing noise, adapting to your surroundings, and making speech easier to understand in difficult environments."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001122", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001121", "text": "Can I stream with Unitron hearing aids?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001124", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001123", "text": "Yes! Most modern Unitron hearing aids include Bluetooth® streaming, which means you can connect them directly to your smartphone, tablet, or TV. This lets you enjoy phone calls, music, videos, and other media streamed straight into your hearing aids for clear, personalized sound. You can also use the Unitron app to adjust settings and fine-tune your listening experience anytime."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001126", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001125", "text": "Find the Right Unitron Hearing Aid in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001128", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001127", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we can help you find the Unitron hearing aid that fits your hearing needs and lifestyle. As an authorized Unitron provider in Newport News, VA, Smithfield, VA, and Chesapeake, VA, we are proud to offer the latest models, expert fittings, and personalized care from our hearing instrument specialist."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001130", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001129", "text": "Schedule your consultation today!"}]}]','Unitron Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Unitron hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
INSERT INTO "ec_hearing_aid_brands" ("id","slug","status","author_id","primary_byline_id","created_at","updated_at","published_at","scheduled_at","deleted_at","version","live_revision_id","draft_revision_id","locale","translation_group","title","content","meta_title","meta_description") VALUES('01KS5Y1MEX1CA3ZKRV7AV08W68','hearing-aid/widex','published','01KS5S2H9D5GVDNPH6HQ00BNCN',NULL,'2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z','2026-05-21 19:47:27','2026-05-22T02:51:25.000Z',NULL,NULL,1,'01KS5Y1MEXWG867VZC514P9J4W',NULL,'en','01KS5Y1MEX1CA3ZKRV7AV08W68','Widex Hearing Aids','[{"_type": "block", "_key": "b001132", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001131", "text": "Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Widex hearing aids in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA.", "marks": ["strong", "em"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001134", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001133", "text": "Widex is known worldwide for its clear, natural sound. Widex hearing aids use advanced technology to process sound almost instantly, giving you a more lifelike listening experience without delay. Our audiologist and hearing instrument specialist will help you choose the right Widex hearing aid for your lifestyle and make sure it’s fitted for your best possible hearing."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001136", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001135", "text": "Widex Hearing Aids in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001138", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001137", "text": "Widex Allure"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001140", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001139", "text": "The Widex Allure offers the perfect blend of highly-advanced technology and elegant design. Designed by experts to deliver the most natural hearing experience possible, reconnect with the world and people around you through clear speech, accurate environmental sound processing, and highly intuitive adjustments."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001142", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001141", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001145", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001143", "text": "Powered by the W1 Chip:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001144", "text": "Widex’s fastest chip delivers quick, clear, and natural sound."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001148", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001146", "text": "Allure PureSound™ with ZeroDelay Technology:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001147", "text": "Helps you hear speech without distortion or echo, creating a more lifelike experience."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001151", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001149", "text": "Speech Enhancer Pro:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001150", "text": "Lowers background noise so voices stand out, making conversations easier-even in noisy places."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001154", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001152", "text": "Dynamic Feedback Controller:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001153", "text": "Adapts to your ear’s shape to reduce annoying whistling or squealing sounds."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001157", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001155", "text": "Smooth Streaming:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001156", "text": "Enjoy music, podcasts, and calls with steady sound-no sudden volume changes or outside interference."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001160", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001158", "text": "Widex Allure App:", "marks": ["strong"]}, {"_type": "span", "_key": "s001159", "text": "Easily adjust settings and personalize your hearing experience right from your smartphone."}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001162", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001161", "text": "Widex SmartRIC"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001164", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001163", "text": "The Widex SmartRIC is one of Widex’s newest hearing aids, designed to deliver natural, lifelike sound in a slim, stylish design. It processes sound almost instantly, so voices and everyday noises feel clear and natural without delay or distortion. What makes SmartRIC stand out is its sleek, modern shape that sits comfortably behind the ear, even when wearing glasses or masks. It’s small, discreet, and designed for all-day comfort. This hearing aid is recommended for people with mild to severe hearing loss."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001166", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001165", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001168", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001167", "text": "The Widex Moment app allows for easy personalization and fine-tuning of settings"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001170", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001169", "text": "Bluetooth streaming works with both iPhone and Android devices"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001172", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001171", "text": "Tinnitus relief is available through Widex Zen Therapy, offering a soothing soundscape"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001174", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001173", "text": "The portable charger offers up to a full week of on-the-go power"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001176", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001175", "text": "Widex Moment Sheer RIC"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001178", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001177", "text": "The Widex Moment Sheer RIC is a receiver-in-canal hearing aid designed to deliver the most natural sound possible. This device blends elegant design with advanced features. It’s slim, discreet, and comfortable to wear all day. Stay connected and confident in any environment with Widex Moment Sheer!"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001180", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001179", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001182", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001181", "text": "Compatible with iOS and Android for effortless Bluetooth pairing"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001184", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001183", "text": "The Widex Moment app allows for customized sound and comfort preferences"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001186", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001185", "text": "Zen Tinnitus Therapy provides calming sounds to ease tinnitus symptoms"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001188", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001187", "text": "Battery life extends up to 29 hours without streaming and approximately 16 hours with moderate streaming"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001190", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001189", "text": "Widex Moment RIC"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001192", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001191", "text": "The Widex Moment RIC is designed to give you natural, lifelike sound in a comfortable receiver-in-canal style. Thanks to Widex PureSound™ technology, it processes sound so quickly that voices, music, and everyday noises feel clear and real, without the “tinny” or artificial sound some hearing aids produce. Moment RIC is slim, discreet, and comfortable for all-day wear. Ideal for people with mild to severe hearing loss, the Widex Moment RIC combines natural sound, modern convenience, and comfort."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001194", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001193", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001196", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001195", "text": "Offers both rechargeable and disposable battery options"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001198", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001197", "text": "Supports Bluetooth streaming for seamless device connectivity"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001200", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001199", "text": "Includes tinnitus relief through built-in Zen programs"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001202", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001201", "text": "The Widex Moment app provides smartphone-based sound adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001204", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001203", "text": "Widex Moment BTE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001206", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001205", "text": "The Widex Moment BTE is a behind-the-ear hearing aid designed to give you powerful, natural sound in a durable and comfortable style. This model is built for those who need more powerful amplification. The BTE design is easy to handle, comfortable to wear, and reliable for all-day use. This is recommended for people with moderate to severe hearing loss as it combines strong performance, natural sound, and modern convenience."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001208", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001207", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001210", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001209", "text": "Bluetooth connectivity supports streaming from smartphones and other devices"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001212", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001211", "text": "Sound settings can be customized through the Moment app"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001214", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001213", "text": "Zen therapy offers integrated tinnitus relief options"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001216", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001215", "text": "Available with rechargeable or traditional size 13 batteries"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001218", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001217", "text": "Widex Moment CROS"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001220", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001219", "text": "The Widex Moment CROS is designed for people with single-sided deafness (SSD) who cannot benefit from a hearing aid in one ear. It works by picking up sounds from your non-hearing side and wirelessly transmitting them to a hearing aid in your better ear. This way, you can hear from both sides, stay more aware of your surroundings, and follow conversations with less effort. The device is slim, discreet, and comfortable to wear all day. For those with single-sided hearing loss, the Widex Moment CROS offers a simple yet powerful solution that restores balance and helps you reconnect with the world around you."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001222", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001221", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001224", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001223", "text": "Can be configured for both CROS and BiCROS setups"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001226", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001225", "text": "Designed to be energy efficient with lower power consumption"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001228", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001227", "text": "Integrates easily with other Widex Moment hearing aids"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001230", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001229", "text": "Widex Moment ITE"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001232", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001231", "text": "The Widex Moment ITE is a custom in-the-ear hearing aid designed to give you clear, natural sound in a discreet style that fits directly in your ear. The Moment ITE processes sound instantly so speech and everyday noises feel lifelike and natural, without the “hearing aid sound” that older models can produce. Despite its small size, the Widex Moment ITE offers modern features like Bluetooth® connectivity for streaming calls, music, and TV audio directly to your hearing aids."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001234", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001233", "text": "Key Features:", "marks": ["strong"]}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001236", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001235", "text": "Custom-fit design ensures a secure and personalized fit"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001238", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001237", "text": "Supports Bluetooth streaming and app-based adjustments"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001240", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001239", "text": "Powered by size 10 or 312 disposable batteries with up to 150 hours of use"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001242", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001241", "text": "Offers built-in Zen Tinnitus Therapy for soothing soundscapes"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001244", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001243", "text": "Widex Assistive Listening Accessories"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001246", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001245", "text": "Take your hearing experience further with accessories designed to improve communication and convenience:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001248", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001247", "text": "Widex TV Play streams high-quality audio directly from your television to your hearing aids • Widex Sound Assist functions as a microphone, remote control, and hands-free calling device • Com-Dex, RC-Dex, and TV-Dex provide additional ways to control your hearing aids and stay connected"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001250", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001249", "text": "Older Widex Models We Support"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001252", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001251", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we continue to service and repair a range of older Widex hearing aids, including:"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001254", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001253", "text": "Widex Evoke"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001256", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001255", "text": "Widex Beyond"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001258", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001257", "text": "Widex Unique"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001260", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001259", "text": "Widex Dream"}], "listItem": "bullet", "level": 1}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001262", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001261", "text": "If you have an older model, contact us to see how we can help maintain or repair your device."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001264", "style": "h3", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001263", "text": "Frequently Asked Questions – Widex Hearing Aids"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001266", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001265", "text": "How long do Widex hearing aids last?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001268", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001267", "text": "On average, Widex hearing aids last about 3 to 5 years. Their lifespan depends on the specific model, how often they’re worn, and the level of care they receive. With regular cleaning and routine check-ups, many people are able to enjoy reliable use for several years."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001270", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001269", "text": "Do Widex hearing aids offer tinnitus relief?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001272", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001271", "text": "Yes. Many Widex devices include Zen Therapy, which plays soft soundscapes or relaxation tones. These gentle sounds can help reduce the awareness of tinnitus and bring a sense of calm during the day."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001274", "style": "h4", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001273", "text": "Can I stream phone calls and music with Widex hearing aids?"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001276", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001275", "text": "Yes. Most modern Widex hearing aids have Bluetooth® connectivity, allowing you to stream calls, music, and other audio straight from iPhone and many Android devices. With the Widex Moment app, you can also adjust settings, change listening programs, and control volume right from your smartphone. Our audiologist and hearing instrument specialist in Newport News, VA, Chesapeake, VA, and Smithfield, VA can help you set everything up with ease."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001278", "style": "h2", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001277", "text": "Find the Right Widex Hearing Aid in Virginia"}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001280", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001279", "text": "At Maico Audiological Services, we’re more than happy to help you find the Widex hearing aid that’s right for your hearing needs, lifestyle, and budget. As an authorized Widex provider in Smithfield, VA, Newport News, VA, and Chesapeake, VA, we offer the latest models, personalized fittings, and long-term support."}]}, {"_type": "block", "_key": "b001282", "style": "normal", "children": [{"_type": "span", "_key": "s001281", "text": "Contact us today to schedule a consultation and experience what Widex technology can do for your hearing!"}]}]','Widex Hearing Aids | Maico Audiological Services','Maico Audiological Services is an authorized provider of Widex hearing aids in Virginia. Contact us to learn more!');
